            <title>[CASSANDRA-17709] CQL.textile needs to be made current</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17709</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Per &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17570&quot; title=&quot;Update the CQL version for the 4.1 release&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17570&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17570&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/doc/cql3/CQL.textile&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/doc/cql3/CQL.textile&lt;/a&gt; is outdated, and the document we ship inside packages, so this should be made current.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
